    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用描绘了hololive成员的“原创花札”游玩的冒险游戏！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴什么是花札🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花札是一种在日本拥有悠久传统，深受男女老少喜爱的卡牌游戏。本游戏设有新手教程和辅助功能，即使是不懂花札规则的玩家也可以安心游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴与hololive成员一起用“新规则”玩怀旧的花札游戏！🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在花札的基本规则“来来”、“追丁株”、“花合”的基础上，还加入了本游戏原创的颠覆常识的全新规则“holo合”。通过集齐牌面上绘制的角色来触发“holo役”，并结合每个角色所拥有的“角色技能”，与对手展开得分对决，热热闹闹地一较高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/5ace7e215c66fb23c9a99e5600798dcf.poster.avif?t=1766631352\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/5ace7e215c66fb23c9a99e5600798dcf.webm?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/5ace7e215c66fb23c9a99e5600798dcf.mp4?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/de1b0556600b3369dff40c9a021662bd.poster.avif?t=1766631352\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/de1b0556600b3369dff40c9a021662bd.webm?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/de1b0556600b3369dff40c9a021662bd.mp4?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴用收集到的点数来制作“原创便当”🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以亲手制作当做“礼品”的便当。甚至还能做出充满hololive爱的创意便当……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/20355bc761dd6d2b057009a67877cc8e.poster.avif?t=1766631352\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/20355bc761dd6d2b057009a67877cc8e.webm?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/20355bc761dd6d2b057009a67877cc8e.mp4?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴在线对战🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了可以和AI对战之外，也可以轻松进行在线对战。不论是和远方的朋友，还是通过随机匹配与陌生人，都能展开对战。还可以和其他用户交换便当哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴出场角色🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>😈百鬼绫目</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“各位人类好呀！呀吼！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隶属于魔界学校的和风鬼娘。喜欢恶作剧，经常放出鬼火戏弄他人为乐。别看她这样，其实她可是学生会长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌽白上吹雪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“狐狐有礼了！我是白上吹雪！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白发兽耳的宅狐。喜欢与人交流，如果和她互动，她会很开心。每天都开开心心地生活，同时努力成为顶级宅系偶像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌲大神澪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“晚上好哦！我是大神澪！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不知从何处突然闪现的黑发兽耳少女。据说经常出没于神社。非常喜欢游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌸樱巫女</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“喵Hello！精英巫女偶像樱巫女来喽！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电脑樱神社的巫女。怀抱对偶像的憧憬，每天都在努力奋斗，立志成为独一无二的顶级精英巫女偶像！虽然自称为精英，但在粉丝之间却流传着她其实是个废物的传闻……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增hololive成员参战的DLC也将上线!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎴剧情🎴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某个偶然的契机下，hololive成员们闯入了一个“遍布着花札中所描绘景色的神秘世界”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路上与伙伴们相遇，并通过花札对决向敌人发起挑战。敬请享受hololive成员们精彩活跃的原创剧情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/2bc87a711c28b8763c366c17e1a21e3c.poster.avif?t=1766631352\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/2bc87a711c28b8763c366c17e1a21e3c.webm?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327640/extras/2bc87a711c28b8763c366c17e1a21e3c.mp4?t=1766631352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
